re":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fa86b014145128f22c4452b82b2e90451c63248","tid":1816254,"uid":57634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"點會咁樣開個channel<br />\n你想知佢地諗咩 自己上去問<br />\n前線係唔洗大台發言架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:51:35.000Z","msg":"其實點解唔開得 我反而想問 根本所有言論都比人壟斷晒"},{"pid":"ad3a5bebc30c4d9a85dcf3fc5719230244025222","tid":1816254,"uid":345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"鬼真係唔可以亂捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cde194584b556475edce6b5093b70502278e5cf","tid":1816254,"uid":35364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解咁講</blockquote>因為唔岩聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>笑 jor 叫人唔好捉鬼 點知個留言就係話鬼 有d sad</blockquote>大家慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂唔順就退場比人捉多最後一次鬼</blockquote><br />\n國安又扮失蹤會員「知更鳥」想洗底，<br />\n知更鳥本人於 10.12 上香園圍探險，<br />\n上山途中聲稱俾狗逗，離奇神秘消失，<br />\n承諾講述香園圍狀況，卻又突然刪文。<br />\n五日後上水態度反常，疑為國安控制。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>【失蹤會員檔案】LorraineC 資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661602</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V99AMr8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV99AMr8.png&h=0a793e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8PEtE3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8PEtE3.png&h=e36b1195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"38b0ea4aae53be1f5907cf17730a3e85d50d443f","tid":1816254,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"760bf2e66b69551edd19cd59681cd4ca81cb3798","tid":1816254,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b89dfc9179a034c589cb668698589d07145bee5","tid":1816254,"uid":193072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2